      "reference_verse_match": {
        "verse_ref": "6.32",
        "sanskrit_devanagari": "आत्मौपम्येन सर्वत्र समं पश्यति योऽर्जुन। सुखं वा यदि वा दुःखं स योगी परमो मतः॥",
        "sanskrit_iast": "ātmaupamyena sarvatra samaṁ paśyati yo'rjuna | sukhaṁ vā yadi vā duḥkhaṁ sa yogī paramo mataḥ ||",
        "hindi_translation": "हे अर्जुन! जो योगी अपनी तरह सब प्राणियों में समान देखता है — चाहे सुख हो या दुःख — वही सर्वश्रेष्ठ माना गया है।",
        "english_translation": "He who sees every being as his own self, and who regards their joy and sorrow as his own — that yogi, O Arjuna, is held to be supreme.",
