        "why_it_applies": "Envy's root is the belief that her gain is your loss. The verse offers the opposite posture — not as a moral command, but as the actual exit from the feeling. Her win, genuinely felt as yours, ends the math the envy is trying to solve.",
        "match_confidence": 0.85
      }
